trans-unit.source: Provides an interface to manage the images, ToolTips, and event handlers for the properties of a component displayed in a property browser.
trans-unit.target: Gir et grensesnitt for å administrere bilder, verktøytips og hendelsesbehandling for egenskaper for en komponent som vises i en nettleser for egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: A component can use the IPropertyValueUIService interface to provide <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem> objects for any properties of the component.
trans-unit.target: En komponent kan bruke grensesnittet IPropertyValueUIService til å angi <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem>objekter for egenskaper av komponenten.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem> associated with a property can provide an image, a ToolTip and an event handler for the event that is raised when the image associated with the property is clicked.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem>knyttet til en egenskap kan gi et bilde, verktøytips og hendelsesbehandling for hendelsen oppstår når bildet som er forbundet med egenskapen klikkes.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem>

trans-unit.source: The IPropertyValueUIService interface provides methods to add, remove, and retrieve <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler> delegates to or from an internal list.
trans-unit.target: Grensesnittet IPropertyValueUIService inneholder metoder for å legge til, fjerne og hente <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler>Representanter til eller fra en intern liste.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler>

trans-unit.source: When the properties of a component are displayed in a property browser, each <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler> in the list is given an opportunity to provide a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem> for each property of the component.
trans-unit.target: Når egenskaper for en komponent som skal vises i en nettleser for egenskapen hver <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler>i listen er angitt en mulighet til å angi en <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem>for hver egenskap for komponenten.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler>

trans-unit.source: When a property browser is set to display the properties of an object, it calls the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.GetPropertyUIValueItems%2A> method of this interface for each property of the component, passing a <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> that represents the property.
trans-unit.target: Når en nettleser for egenskapen er satt til å vise egenskaper for et objekt, kaller den <xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.GetPropertyUIValueItems%2A>metode for dette grensesnittet for hver egenskap av komponenten sending av en <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>som representerer egenskapen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.GetPropertyUIValueItems%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.GetPropertyUIValueItems%2A> method calls each <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler> that has been added to the service.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.GetPropertyUIValueItems%2A>metodekall hver <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler>som er lagt til tjenesten.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.GetPropertyUIValueItems%2A>

trans-unit.source: Each <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler> can add a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem> to the <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> parameter passed in the `valueUIItemList` parameter to supply UI items for the property represented by the <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> passed in the `propDesc` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Hver <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler>kan legge til en <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem>til den <xref:System.Collections.ArrayList>parameteren ble sendt i den `valueUIItemList` som parameter for levering Brukergrensesnittet for egenskapen representert av den <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>sendt den `propDesc` parameteren.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> </xref:System.Collections.ArrayList> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem> can contain an image to display next to the property name, a ToolTip string, and an event handler to invoke when an image associated with the property is double-clicked.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem>kan inneholde et bilde som skal vises ved siden av egenskapsnavnet, en verktøytips streng og hendelsesbehandling for å aktivere når du et bilde som er forbundet med egenskapen dobbeltklikker.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem>

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler"></xref> to this service.
trans-unit.target: Legger til den angitte <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler"> </xref> til denne tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: When <xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.GetPropertyUIValueItems%2A> is called, each handler added to this service is called and given the opportunity to add an icon for the property.
trans-unit.target: Når <xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.GetPropertyUIValueItems%2A>er kalt, hver behandlingsprogrammet som er lagt til denne tjenesten er kallet og muligheten til å legge til et ikon for egenskapen.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.GetPropertyUIValueItems%2A>

trans-unit.source: The property value UI handler to add.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen verdi, UI-behandlingsprogrammet å legge til.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem"></xref> objects that match the specified context and property descriptor characteristics.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem"> </xref> objekter som samsvarer med angitt sammenheng og egenskapen sikkerhetsbeskrivelse egenskapene.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som kan brukes til å få ytterligere kontekstinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor"></xref> that indicates the property to match with the properties to return.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor"> </xref> som angir egenskapen som samsvarer med egenskapene til å returnere.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem"></xref> objects that match the specified parameters.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem"> </xref> objekter som samsvarer med de angitte parameterne.

trans-unit.source: Notifies the <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService"></xref> implementation that the global list of <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem"></xref> objects has been modified.
trans-unit.target: Varsler den <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService"> </xref> implementering som den globale listen over <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem"> </xref> objekter har blitt endret.

trans-unit.source: Occurs when the list of <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem"></xref> objects is modified.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når listen over <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem"> </xref> objekter er endret.

trans-unit.source: Components that serve <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem> objects can call <xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.NotifyPropertyValueUIItemsChanged%2A> when they change their list of items.
trans-unit.target: Komponenter som fungerer <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem>objekter kan ringe <xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.NotifyPropertyValueUIItemsChanged%2A>når de endre listen over elementer.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.IPropertyValueUIService.NotifyPropertyValueUIItemsChanged%2A> </xref:System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIItem>

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som skal legges til.

trans-unit.source: Removes the specified <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler"></xref> from the property value UI service.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner det angitte <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PropertyValueUIHandler"> </xref> fra egenskapsverdi UI-tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The handler to remove.
trans-unit.target: Et behandlingsprogram til å fjerne.
